{"tid":670447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體冀紅色小巴納入兩元乘車優惠","createTime":"2018-05-19T11:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T06:38:18.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5d00880547dacb09762e2fcc425a829dbc84e0","tid":670447,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有小巴團體促請政府，將紅色小巴納入長者及傷殘人士兩元乘車優惠計劃。<br />\n<br />\n公共小巴車主司機協進總會十多名代表，到政府總部外請願。<br />\n<br />\n團體指，部分紅色小巴營運手法與綠色小巴手法大致相同，希望政府將紅色小巴納入兩元的長者及傷殘人士票價優惠計劃，既可惠及市民，又可改善紅色小巴的營商環境，打破紅巴逐漸被邊緣化的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n對於有意見擔心紅色小巴收費浮動，令政府難以確保公幣運用得宜。立法會航運交通界議員易志明表示，業界願意和政府協商，以最低收費來釐定補貼。"},{"pid":"8ddddea41f049509ec584a5a477481bd94954cf0","tid":670447,"uid":37733,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"自己係咁嘟 渣車都慳返"},{"pid":"d64dd1009391a6ec5e24212ff3a16f1ee6039310","tid":670447,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"條街咪冇撚哂紅巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a28eb0cc26b929dee4a55aefe2d3d88e15f4a9","tid":670447,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"長者收100"},{"pid":"cfed4766b522dac40786b62a0480fa89d046a105","tid":670447,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64dd1009391a6ec5e24212ff3a16f1ee6039310","tid":670447,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"條街咪冇撚哂紅巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"去茶記門口一邊歎茶一邊嘟啦"},{"pid":"b04c6c5aec1f0b272ddb61acb0ba5fbdd240b035","tid":670447,"uid":60156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"旺角成條街比d 紅van霸左又點樣邊緣化呀，係咪要霸多條街先得？"},{"pid":"4cc